@do_own_shit
subtitle: Hindenburg will be our target.
on-arrival: sh_strength -= 1000; old_middle_nsdap -= 5; unemployed_nsdap -= 5; rural_nsdap -= 5; old_middle_dnvp -= 50; new_middle_dnvp -= 50; unemployed_dnvp -= 50; rural_dnvp -= 50; catholics_dnvp -= 50; workers_dnvp -= 50; workers_sdp += 10; unemployed_sdp += 5; catholics_sdp += 5; rural_sdp += 5;

We staged our own incident with the reichbanner on opposition leaders. Most importantly, Hindenburg was our target, as he stood in our way of absolute power. We staged a incident, where one of our guys pretended to be an Stahlhelm officer who would assasinate the incumbent president, who worked at the order of the DVNP. This gave the court a reason to percecute the DNVP. 
